Type: Package
Package: comorbidity
Version: 0.0.3
Title: Computing Comorbidity Scores
Description: Computing comorbidity scores such as the weighted Charlson score (Charlson 1987, PMID: 3558716) and the
 Elixhauser comorbidity score (Elixhauser 1998, PMID: 9431328) using ICD-10 codes (Quan 2005, PMID: 16224307).
